events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-05 Crystal Palace vs Arsenal
events.strDescriptionEN: The Premier is back! After a few eternal weeks without club football, the best league in the world is here. Crystal Palace and Arsenal are in charge of kicking off this new season. A high-level match between two Premier League classics!

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-06 Fulham vs Liverpool
events.strDescriptionEN: JÃ¼rgen Klopp's Liverpool, who arrive at the event after winning the Community Shield, the first title of the course, opens this Premier League season by visiting Craven Cottage, where the newly promoted, although classic in the competition, awaits them, Fulham . As classic as its old stadium.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-06 Bournemouth vs Aston Villa
events.strDescriptionEN: Bournemouth and Aston Villa begin their participation in the current edition of the Premier League measuring forces at the Vitality Stadium. Curiously, Bournemouth's premiere in the Premier was against the villains in 2015.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-06 Leeds vs Wolves
events.strDescriptionEN: Leeds United, who suffered excessively last season to achieve permanence, and Wolverhampton begin their journey in the new season of the Premier League facing each other at Elland Road. Wolves ended last season on a losing run on the road and haven't won away from home in the league since March.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-06 Tottenham vs Southampton
events.strDescriptionEN: Tottenham faces an important season, in which they will participate in the Champions League, and they do so in the domestic championship making their debut against Southampton at home. The duo formed by Kane (11) and Son (10) have 21 goals against Soton. One of the favorite prey of the Spurs offensive tandem.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-06 Everton vs Chelsea
events.strDescriptionEN: Chelsea opens fire this Premier League season at Goodison Park to face off against Everton who want to leave behind what they suffered last season. The last four visits of the blues to the toffee stadium. This is the Londoners' worst current run with any English club.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-06 Newcastle vs Nottingham Forest
events.strDescriptionEN: The historic Nottingham Forest, which returns to the Premier League this season since relegation from the top English competition in 1999, debuts against the always difficult Newcastle at St James Park, who also have Forest as one of their favorite victims.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-07 Leicester vs Brentford
events.strDescriptionEN: Leicester and Brentford meet at the King Power Stadium on the first day of the new Premier League season. Vardy, the top scorer in the history of the Foxes, is only 17 goals away from 150 goals and thus enters the top-10 of the Premier's top scorers.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-07 Manchester United vs Brighton
events.strDescriptionEN: Manchester United need to return to the elite of the Premier League after a disastrous season in which they had to settle for sixth place and with empty hands of titles. Their debut is this season, at Old Trafford against Brighton, a rival that still doesn't know what it's like to win at the Theater of Dreams. Will the streak continue?

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-07 West Ham vs Manchester City
events.strDescriptionEN: Manchester City, led by Erling-Braut Haaland, begins the defense of its Premier League title won last season at the London Stadium, where a West Ham team that wants to fight for Europe awaits. City are undefeated in their last 13 Premier games with the hammers (W10 and D3), and only against Fulham (14) are they on a longer unbeaten streak between teams in the 2022/23 Premier!

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-13 Arsenal vs Leicester
English Premier League 2022-08-13 Aston Villa vs Everton
events.strDescriptionEN: Steven Gerrard's Aston Villa side welcome Everton to Villa Park in the Premier League.

English Premier League 2022-08-13 Manchester City vs Bournemouth

English Premier League 2022-08-20 Bournemouth vs Arsenal
events.strDescriptionEN: Arsenal visits Bournemouth's home on matchday three of the Premier with a Gabriel JesÃºs in a state of thanks after his brace against Leicester. The local team arrives at the match after a tough defeat against Manchester City.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-20 Crystal Palace vs Aston Villa
English Premier League 2022-08-20 Fulham vs Brentford
English Premier League 2022-08-20 Leicester vs Southampton
English Premier League 2022-08-20 Tottenham vs Wolves
events.strDescriptionEN: Tottenham and Wolverhampton open the third day of the Premier League. The Spurs arrive at the meeting after drawing an in extremis draw against Chelsea at Stanford Brigde, thanks to a goal from Harry Kane. For their part, the Wolves go to the Tottenham Hotspur Stadium after drawing 0-0 at home against Fulham.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-20 Everton vs Nottingham Forest
English Premier League 2022-08-21 Leeds vs Chelsea
events.strDescriptionEN: Elland Road hosts the meeting between Leeds United and Chelsea corresponding to the third day of the Premier League. Both teams come to the meeting after adding a point in the last day.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-21 Newcastle vs Manchester City
English Premier League 2022-08-21 West Ham vs Brighton
English Premier League 2022-08-22 Manchester United vs Liverpool
events.strDescriptionEN: The England classic is here! Manchester United and Liverpool face each other in a real match in which each team goes through very different dynamics. The Red Devils still do not know the victory in this Premier League and come from a blushing 4-0 against Brentford. For its part, Jurgen Klopp's team, without Darwin NuÃ±ez, arrives at Old Trafford after drawing against Crystal Palace last day.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-27 Arsenal vs Fulham
events.strDescriptionEN: Arsenal wants to continue the streak, they already have three of three, in the second London derby of this campaign. Fulham are bad at Gunners. They have only added three wins out of 30 duels against their neighbors and never as visitors.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-27 Brentford vs Everton
English Premier League 2022-08-27 Brighton vs Leeds
English Premier League 2022-08-27 Chelsea vs Leicester
events.strDescriptionEN: Although Leicester are not traditionally good at Chelsea at Stamford Bridge, the Foxes have chased great results in their recent visits to the blue fiefdom, both in the FA Cup and the Premier League.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-27 Liverpool vs Bournemouth
events.strDescriptionEN: Bournemouth have never won at Anfield Road. In fact, they have only managed one goal in their last five games against a much-needed Liverpool side. And it is that the Reds have not yet won this season in the Premier.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-27 Manchester City vs Crystal Palace
events.strDescriptionEN: Crystal Palace is one of the great killers of the Premier. The glaziers tend to score quite a few times at the home of the Big-6 teams. Not surprisingly, they have beaten City at the Etihad in 2018 and 2021.

events.strFilename: English Premier League 2022-08-27 Southampton vs Manchester United
events.strDescriptionEN: Southampton hosts Cristiano Ronaldo's Manchester United, and also Casemiro's, on matchday four of the Premier League. New litmus test for the Red Devils, who have no margin for error if they want to stick to the top of the rankings.
